==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perrier
<hw>Per"ri*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF. <ets>perriere</ets>, <ets>perrier</ets>, F. <ets>perrier</ets>.  Cf. <er>Pederero</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Mil.)</fld> <def>A short mortar used formerly for throwing stone shot.</def>  <rj><au>Hakluyt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Perrier</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Perrier
<hw>Per"ri*er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos>  <def>The name of a brand of bottled mineral water; a glass or bottle of such water; <as>as, I'll have a <ex>Perrier</ex>.</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Perron</ent>⟦br⟧
